        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="current" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EFF6FF;strokeColor=#3B82F6;align=left;spacingLeft=16;fontSize=14" value="当前状态&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• V3.5 baseline 已冻结&lt;br&gt;• V3.6-A 到 J 已完成并通过 Dummy Pipeline E2E&lt;br&gt;• Preflight hardening 已完成：scope guard、legacy approval guard、high-risk patch governance、Board job scope check、business EventBridge permission&lt;br&gt;• EventBridge follow mode 已补齐新增事件轮询；subscription token 绑定 origin&lt;br&gt;• business event idempotency marker 与 context update 原子应用；duplicate binding_id 被拒绝&lt;br&gt;• Platform startup neutrality：Gateway 顶层不 hard import Meeting/Knowledge/Video workflow&lt;br&gt;• 当前允许声明：V3.6/V4.0 preflight hardening complete&lt;br&gt;• 仍不得声明：Workflow Studio ready / AgentTalkWindow ready / production-ready external app support / distributed workflow engine ready" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="210" width="590" x="100" y="1100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="gap" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFBEB;strokeColor=#F59E0B;align=left;spacingLeft=16;fontSize=14" value="核心差距&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• V3.6 后端 gate 已关闭：Dummy Pipeline E2E + preflight hardening 通过&lt;br&gt;• quality.evaluated 仍为 trace-only，不声明 live streaming ready&lt;br&gt;• V4.0 具备启动条件，但本轮仍暂停 V4.0-0 实施&lt;br&gt;• Workflow Studio / AgentTalkWindow 仍需 V4.0 实现&lt;br&gt;• production workflow automation 和 distributed engine 仍非当前声明" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="210" width="590" x="805" y="1100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="target" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ECFDF5;strokeColor=#059669;align=left;spacingLeft=16;fontSize=14" value="V3.6 目标状态&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Workflow runtime objects 成为一等对象&lt;br&gt;• StationRun 可追踪输入、输出、审批、质量、失败&lt;br&gt;• Board API 可重建完整流水线状态&lt;br&gt;• Agent 只能 propose patch，apply 只影响 draft&lt;br&gt;• V4.0 UI 可消费真实后端事实源" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="210" width="590" x="1510" y="1100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="eg1" edge="1" parent="1" source="current" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;strokeColor=#0284C7;endArrow=block;endFill=1" target="gap">
